        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">AI visibility monitoring platform with agency services. Productised approach with Snapshot Audit, Advanced Audit, and ongoing monitoring. Dashboard product for tracking AI mentions across platforms. SaaS-style pricing from GBP 100/mo. The monitoring dashboard provides a low-commitment way for Glasgow businesses to understand their AI visibility position before investing in a full engagement.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Strengths:</span> Productised approach. Dashboard for ongoing monitoring. Transparent pricing. Early mover in UK AI visibility space.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">awarenessai.co.uk</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 3. Exposure Ninja -->
