      <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">Glasgow's economy is built on creative industries, engineering, financial services, and a thriving food and drink sector. The city has a strong digital marketing community, but AI search visibility remains a new discipline that most local agencies have not yet developed expertise in.</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">For Glasgow businesses, the practical path to AI search visibility is working with UK-wide specialists remotely. AI search work is delivered digitally by nature. Platform testing, content optimisation, entity architecture, and structured data implementation do not require face-to-face meetings. The depth of an agency's AI methodology is what determines results, not office location.</p>
